                <p>Research goals: 
                    <ol>
                        <li>Investigate the impact of TSCF GRFP Bootcamp on URM performance on fellowships </li>
                        <li>Investigate the impacts of TSCF Professional Experiences on URM performance on applications to REUs, graduate school, and STEM workforce opportunities </li>
                        <li>Investigate the impact of the TSCF on motivations to continue in STEM Fields</li>
                    </ol>
                    
